追随者发动罢工尽他们所能。 “伊斯兰之狮：追逐你的猎物，无论是犹太人、基督徒还是他们的盟友，”<small>;ISKP</small>; 一月份敦促道。</p>;<p data-component="paragraph" class="css-1f0x4sl e1tt35bk0" >;那么接下来怎么办？挪威国防研究机构的 Petter Nesser 表示，欧洲的圣战阴谋，无论成功还是失败，都会随着哈里发国的衰落而减弱（见图 1）。</p>;<div class="css-1m7l96h e18kpe851">;<figure类=“css-1njzmap e1197rjj0”>;<img加载=“惰性”宽度=“608”高度=“817”解码=“异步”data-nimg=“1”样式=“颜色：透明”尺寸=“300px” srcset =“https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=16，quality=80，format=auto/content-assets/images/20240504_EPC031.png 16w，https://www.economist。 com/cdn-cgi/image/width=32，quality=80，format=auto/content-assets/images/20240504_EPC031.png 32w，https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=48 ,quality=80,format=auto/content-assets/images/20240504_EPC031.png 48w, https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=64,quality=80,format=auto/content-资产/图像/20240504_EPC031.png 64w，https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=96，quality=80，format=auto/content-assets/images/20240504_EPC031.png 96w，https： //www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=128，quality=80，format=auto/content-assets/images/20240504_EPC031.png 128w，https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi /image/width=256，quality=80，format=auto/content-assets/images/20240504_EPC031.png 256w，https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=360，quality=80，格式=自动/内容资产/图像/20240504_EPC031.png 360w，https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=384，质量=80，格式=自动/内容资产/图像/20240504_EPC031 .png 384w，https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=480，quality=80，format=auto/content-assets/images/20240504_EPC031.png 480w，https://www.economist .com/cdn-cgi/image/width=600，quality=80，format=auto/content-assets/images/20240504_EPC031.png 600w，https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width= 834，质量= 80，格式=自动/内容资产/图像/20240504_EPC031.png 834w，https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=960，质量= 80，格式=自动/内容-assets/images/20240504_EPC031.png 960w，https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=1096，quality=80，format=auto/content-assets/images/20240504_EPC031.png 1096w，https ://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/wi